headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires The Equinox Agency, LLC
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Emmaus, Pennsylvania-based Equinox Agency, LLC. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
